OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage is
OL,7,Funveiling his party's plan to tackle
OL,8,Fthe small boats crisis on Tuesday,
OL,9,Fpromising mass deportations and an
OL,10,Foverhaul of human rights law if his
OL,11,Fparty wins the next election.
OL,13,FDubbed 'Operation Restoring Justice',
OL,14,Fthe party says the plan is a "five
OL,15,Fyear emergency programme to track
OL,16,Fdown, detain and deport all illegal
OL,17,Fmigrants in the United Kingdom."
