OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FAt a press conference in Oxfordshire,
OL,7,FFarage announced his party would leave
OL,8,Fthe European Convention on Human
OL,9,FRights and scrap the Human Rights Act
OL,10,Fto prevent legal challenges.
OL,12,FThe party aims to replace the Human
OL,13,FRights Act with a British Bill of
OL,14,FRights, which would only apply to
OL,15,FBritish citizens and those who have a
OL,16,Flegal right to live in the UK.
OL,18,FWatch Nigel Farage's press conference
OL,19,Fin full.
