OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FWhile Reform only have four MPs in
OL,7,FParliament, polls over the past few
OL,8,Fmonths put the party around 30%.
OL,10,FDelivering a speech as part of the
OL,11,Fannouncement, Farage said: "If you
OL,12,Fcome to the UK illegally, you will be
OL,13,Fdetained and deported and never ever
OL,14,Fallowed to stay."
OL,16,FThe Reform leader described the small
OL,17,Fboats crisis as a "growing threat to
OL,18,Four national security", and a "genuine
OL,19,Fthreat to public order."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
