OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FThe party say they'll launch a new
OL,7,Fenforcement unit called the 'UK
OL,8,FDeportation Command', with asylum
OL,9,Fseekers offered #2,500 to board
OL,10,Fdeportation flights back to the
OL,11,Fcountries they came from, or to third
OL,12,Fcountries such as Rwanda or Albania.
OL,14,FThe party say they would use aid as an
OL,15,Fincentive to countries to take back
OL,16,Fasylum seekers, with further threats
OL,17,Fof blocking visas or introducing
OL,18,Fsanctions if they do not comply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
