OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FThe plan would see migrants housed in
OL,7,Fold military bases before they were
OL,8,Fdeported - the party says these sites
OL,9,Fwould hold 24,000 people within 18
OL,10,Fmonths at a cost of #2.5 billion.
OL,12,FFarage says the whole plan would cost
OL,13,F#10 million, but the government has
OL,14,Fcriticised the announcement as "back-
OL,15,Fof-the-fag-packet plans".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
