OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FWhen pressed about the planned
OL,7,Foverhaul of Britain's international
OL,8,Fobligations to people seeking asylum
OL,9,Fon Good Morning Britain, Reform's Head
OL,10,Fof Government Efficiency Zia Yusuf
OL,11,Finsisted "the human rights of British
OL,12,Fpeople will take precedence."
OL,14,FThe nationalities making up the
OL,15,Fhighest proportions of those claiming
OL,16,Fasylum in the UK are Pakistan,
OL,17,FAfghanistan, Iran, Eritrea and
OL,18,FBangladesh.
