OL,6,FYusuf was also asked about comments by
OL,7,FFarage in an interview with The Times,
OL,8,Fin which he suggested it's not the
OL,9,Fresponsibility of the British
OL,10,Fgovernment if people returned to
OL,11,FAfghanistan are tortured or killed by
OL,12,Fthe Taliban.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately, there are despotic
OL,15,Fregimes in the world, as Nigel said
OL,16,Fvery clearly in that interview, and we
OL,17,Fmake no apologies for this. The
OL,18,FBritish prime minister cannot be held
OL,19,Fresponsible for the actions of
OL,20,Fdespotic regimes all over the world,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
