OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FFarage has been criticised for
OL,7,Fpreviously saying mass deportations
OL,8,Fare a "political impossibility", but
OL,9,FYusuf told BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,10,Fprogramme the party leader has
OL,11,F"changed his mind".
OL,13,FConcern about the small boats crisis
OL,14,Fand community tensions triggered by
OL,15,Fthe number of asylum seekers living in
OL,16,Fhotels has mounted in recent weeks.
OL,18,FProtests at an asylum hotel in Epping
OL,19,Fsparked a further wave of protests
OL,20,Facross the UK, which continued at the
OL,21,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
