OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FThe government is braced for further
OL,7,Flegal fights over the use of hotels,
OL,8,Fafter Epping Forest Council won a High
OL,9,FCourt challenge against the use of the
OL,10,FBell Hotel for asylum seekers.
OL,12,FITV News understands at least 30 other
OL,13,Fcouncils are considering the
OL,14,Fimplications of the Epping Ruling,
OL,15,Fwith many actively looking at legal
OL,16,Faction.
