OL,3,CReform announce plan to tackle small
OL,4,Cboats crisis through mass deportations
OL,6,FThe government is reportedly ready to
OL,7,Fsend more than 100 small boats
OL,8,Farrivals back across the Channel as
OL,9,Fpart of Sir Keir Starmer's one-in-one-
OL,10,Fout pilot deal with France, according
OL,11,Fto The Times.
OL,13,FThe newspaper reported that a group of
OL,14,F100-plus migrants currently in
OL,15,Fdetention, including some arrested
OL,16,Fover the weekend, could be among the
OL,17,Ffirst to be sent back to France under
OL,18,Fthe scheme.
